-- Espirito Santo, Caixa Geral to Sell Zon Stakes, Negocios Says
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-03-23T08:01:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-23/espirito-santo-caixa-geral-to-sell-zon-stakes-negocios-says.html
Grupo Espirito Santo and  Caixa
Geral de Depositos  may sell their stakes in  Zon Multimedia SGPS
SA (ZON)  at the same time,  Jornal de Negocios  reported, without saying
how it got the information.  The aim of carrying out the sale simultaneously is for
Espirito Santo and Caixa Geral to maximize the value obtained
from their holdings in Zon, the Portuguese newspaper said.
Espirito Santo and Caixa Geral together own 22 percent of Zon,
Jornal de Negocios said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
 halmeida5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
